#: ../storage/factory-reset.rst:2
msgid "Factory Reset"
msgstr "Restablecimiento de fábrica"

#: ../storage/factory-reset.rst:8
msgid "There are two types of factory resets for Nitrokey Storage devices:"
msgstr ""
"Hay dos tipos de restablecimiento de fábrica para los dispositivos "
"Nitrokey Storage:"

#: ../storage/factory-reset.rst:10
msgid ""
"a factory reset of the OpenPGP smart card, for example using ``gpg "
"--card-edit``, followed by ``admin`` and finally: ``factory-reset``"
msgstr ""
"un restablecimiento de fábrica de la tarjeta inteligente OpenPGP, por "
"ejemplo utilizando ``gpg --card-edit``, seguido de ``admin`` y, por "
"último: ``factory-reset``"

